Duong’ mar Nyasaye


1  Nyasaye ma ngimane ochwere ema ne ochueyo gik moko duto.


2  Ruoth Nyasaye kende ema ni kare.


4  Onge ng’ama nigi teko mar hulo timbene.

Ere ng’ama nyalo fwenyo tiend honni mage?


5  Koso ere ng’ama nyalo ng’eyo tekone miwuoro?

Ere ng’a, ma ditem hulo ng’wonone duto?


6  Onge gima inyalo medo kuomgi, kata golo oko kuomgi.

Honni mag Nyasaye ok nyal fweny tiendgi.


7  Ka ng’ato paro ni osetieko fwenyogi, to kara eka ochako!

To kotieko paro, to wach pod otare mana kaka chon.

Dhano ok gimoro


8  Dhano en ang’o? Koso ere ohala mokelo ni Nyasaye?

Ere berne, kata rachne?


9  Ka hik dhano okadho mia achiel, to mano ng’eny moloyo.


10  To kipimo higni manokgo gi higni ma nyaka chieng’,

to gin mana kaka ton pi achiel molwar e nam,

kata ka kuoyo achiel manie dhonam.


11  Mano emomiyo Ruoth Nyasaye hore mos gi ji,

kotimonigi ng’wono mogundho.


12  Oneno kendo ong’eyo ni gikogi rach moloyo,


13  Dhano bedo mang’won mana ni owadgi kende;

Ruoth Nyasaye to bedo mang’won ni gik mangima duto.

Odwokogi ire, kaka jakwath dwoko rombe,

kokwerogi, kendo konyisogi kethogi, kendo kopuonjogi.


14  Obedo mang’won ni jogo moyie kum momiyogi,

kendo mabedo mamor kawinjo chikene.

Timbe ng’wono


15  Wuoda, kitimo ni ng’ato tim ng’wono, to kik ikekne,

kendo kichiwo gimoro, to kik iketh timni maberno

kimedoe weche makwiny.


16  Kaka koth kueyo liet mar piny,

e kaka wach nyalo bedo maber moloyo mich.


17  Adier, wach ber moloyo mich maduong’,

to ng’ama ng’won oyie chiwo gik moko ariyogo duto.


18  Ng’ama ofuwo to chiwo mana ayany kende,

kendo jachiwo ma jang’ur miyo wang’ bedo mokuyo.

Ber mar horruok mos


19  Kapok iwuyo, to onego ikwong ipuonjri rieko,

kendo kapok idoko matuo, to rit ngimani.


20  Bende kapok bura ochopo, to nonri kendi,

eka iniyud ng’wono chieng’ miyaloe buchi.


21  Bed mobolore kapok iyudo tuo,

kendo kitimo richo, to lokri iwegi piyopiyo.


22  Kik gimoro moni chopo singruokni e kinde mowinjore,

kendo kik irit nyaka chieng’ thoni, eka ilos wecheni.


23  Kapok isingori ni ibiro timo gimoro,

to nyaka ibed moikore mar time,

mondo kik ibed ka ng’ama temo Nyasaye.


24  Pile nyaka ipar ni

Nyasaye nyalo bedo kodi gi mirima chieng’ thoni,

nikech en chieng’ chulo kuor, ma Nyasaye nyalo lokonie ng’eye.


25  E kinde ma in gi chiemo mathoth, to nyaka ipar ndalo kech,

kendo ndalo ma in gi mwandu, to nyaka ipar dhier kod chan.


26  Hawi ma in-go nyalo lokore e kind okinyi godhiambo,

kendo gik moko nyalo lokore mapiyo, ka Nyasaye ema dwaro kamano.


27  Ng’ama riek bedo motang’ ndalo duto,

kendo kata e kinde ma ji timoe richo mang’eny, to en oritore mondo kik okethi.


28  Ng’ato ka ng’ato mariek dwaro medo bedo mariek,

kendo opako ng’ama oyudo rieko.


29  Joma riek kuom wuoyo,

nyiso riekogi ka gigoyo ngeche mabeyo mathoth.

Ritruok


30  Kik iyie gombo mag chunyi loyi, to geng’gi,


31  nikech kitimo gimoro ma chunyi gombo,

to wasiki nonyieri.


32  Kik ibed e ngima mamalo ahinya,

kendo kik iwuothi gi joma nigi ngima ma kamano.


33  Kik itim nyasi gi pesa miholo, ka in to ionge gi gimoro,

nono to idoko jachan chutho makuecho.

